    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve up to an 8,400 RPM redline, sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed manual gearbox and a speed-sensing variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry utilizes forged aluminum control arms and a five-link rear setup to minimize unsprung mass. Mechanically sound with documented rod bearing service and a rigid chassis, this example offers surgical turn-in and the unmistakable acoustic signature of a flat-plane inspired V8. A focused driver's car that balances daily usability with track-bred performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
