      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2017 luxury sport crossover has been meticulously maintained and serves as a perfect blend of performance and utility. The exterior shines in a deep Midnight Blue metallic; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body remains straight and free of major dings. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring supple pebble-gray leather upholstery that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's seat. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and premium navigation system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, backed by a complete service history and a brand-new set of all-season tires. This vehicle drives straight, shifts crisply, and offers the confident handling you expect from a premium brand. It is a well-loved, reliable machine ready for its next chapter.",
